      "layout": "The page structure is full-bleed, adapting to the viewport width, with some sections containing content within a conceptual maximum width via internal left/right padding. The hero sections often feature large, impactful visuals on a dark background with centered, bold headlines. Subsequent sections alternate between light and dark themes, creating visual rhythm. Content is typically arranged in clear, stacked blocks or alternating text-left/image-right (or vice-versa) two-column layouts. Navigation is a persistent top bar featuring the brand logo, primary navigation links, and a prominent call-to-action button, ensuring constant access to key areas. Sections are generously spaced vertically, contributing to a comfortable density.",
      "imagery": "The visual language for imagery is a mix of high-quality product renders, dark-mode focused lifestyle photography, and clean, geometric line icons. Photography tends to be dark and moody with a warm glow, often showing individuals using devices in comfortable, ambient settings, emphasizing privacy and security. Product visuals are crisp and isolated, often placed within abstract or stylized contexts (like the jelly cake). Icons are outlined, conveying functionality without visual clutter, with occasional fills for emphasis. Imagery serves both decorative atmosphere within dark sections and explanatory content within light sections.",
